  "message": "test(conformance): FP-P2D-165/166 head/tail zero-n strict fixtures\n\nAdds two additional edge-case packets for the DataFrame head/tail\naggregation contract that were still untracked after the 30-fixture\nFP-P2D-051..168 sweep:\n\n- fp_p2d_165_dataframe_head_zero_n_strict: head(n=0) on a frame with a\n  duplicate-label index and non-default column_order \u2014 expected result is\n  an empty frame that still reports the duplicate index labels and column\n  order faithfully.\n- fp_p2d_166_dataframe_tail_zero_n_strict: matching zero-n tail contract\n  under the same duplicate-index / reordered-columns setup.\n\nThese round out the \"n = 0 / n = \u00b1|len| / n = -|len|\" boundary coverage\nfor head/tail in strict mode.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.7 (1M context) <noreply@anthropic.com>",
